{"tid":32224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俏女郎爬梯落簷篷　勇救百厭貓咪笑開眉","createTime":"2016-12-10T05:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T02:13:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60d07078029d14f42cc5ee7912d03bdb93eba1ad","tid":32224,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161210/photo/bkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=8dc5a63e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n勇救貓咪的愛心爆棚女郎。(高潤榮攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161210/photo/bkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_02b.jpg&h=8ad6acad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161210/photo/bkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_03b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_03b.jpg&h=9dadb8ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161210/photo/bkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_04b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_04b.jpg&h=f9ccd527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161210/photo/bkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_05b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_05b.jpg&h=eeb7c164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161210/photo/bkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_06b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_06b.jpg&h=d73afda1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161210/photo/bkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_07b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001_07b.jpg&h=c041e9e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=5Cz7%2FRjhriApYT0U1DyvvwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f05089a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 旺角鬧市上演一幕豔麗溫情救貓場面。一隻約2歲大貪玩雌性小家貓「妹妹」，疑被街景吸引，昨晚10時許，於通菜街39號一樓一間賓館的露台爬落約8呎以下簷篷，牠無大礙，惟「有落無上」當場被困，適逢一名<span style=\"color: red;\">樣貌俏麗甜美、曾多次勇救小動物的姓巫女子</span>，到賓館探訪貓咪的女主人，見狀立即報案求助。"},{"pid":"4ac5db4037e19a71cb5f885d526dbd7f06bac084","tid":32224,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22faad1a8e161baedb9c069d634aba3faf474316","tid":32224,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:35:01.000Z","msg":"警員接報到場了解後，召愛協人員到場協助，在視察現場環境後，將一把長梯放於簷篷。惟由於簷篷較薄，負重能力有限，又恐「妹妹」見到陌生人會受驚亂竄，會導致受傷甚至墮樓，巫遂自動請纓親身營救。她在愛協人員協助下做足安全措施，戴上厚手套及將一條安全繩索繫於身上後，小心翼翼爬到簷篷，將「妹妹」擁入懷中，「妹妹」亦乖乖就範。愛協人員隨後放下一個貓籠，貓咪進入籠後，由愛協人員放回賓館安全位置，與主人重聚。巫及後亦動作俐落爬回賓館內，見「妹妹」安然無恙，笑逐顏開。 <br />\n<br />\n愛心爆棚的巫表示，她從事貿易工作，曾在泰國及法國等地居住，以前曾做過救貓狗義工，早前在北京工作時見過一隻跛腳的小狗，狀甚可憐，她立即施以援手。對於勇敢救貓行為獲讚，巫即嫣然一笑，謙虛地說：「(爬梯救貓)唔勇敢，好小事啫，我以前救過野豬添！」 <br />\n<br />\n之後，她娓娓道出救野豬故事，「我以前住北角雲景道，見到野豬畀幾隻狗追，成忽肉爛晒，當時我有打去野豬會」，最終成功將野豬救離險境，交由相關部門處理善後。巫亦透露，獲救貓咪的女主人養有多隻可愛小貓，她對是次能親身救回該隻貓咪，大感安慰。"},{"pid":"92bb708e943aafb7e1f6bd2c900ab0e30782c173","tid":32224,"uid":23019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a5d9342c36737f69d393bb0b2722491157e760","tid":32224,"uid":1391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:36:47.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰"},{"pid":"9d8f76ec5b4990eae53562a7c8a86b9488f8a046","tid":32224,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"通菜街39號"},{"pid":"afbc080f378f7db1a65f9585419e9390c7840bd0","tid":32224,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母北姑雞咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8149eddbd4472043f0b5e779cc378a613395ac99","tid":32224,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:39:01.000Z","msg":"有啲似老撚左既高海寧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4460c71f91386a42ec67d097825af4eea078475","tid":32224,"uid":44840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef8474f46326c11067e19700e4914611016e217","tid":32224,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大個你個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9629a6f7ec86f517bff9422123affd7de2edbd10","tid":32224,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"141"},{"pid":"cddbe11942cbf15be5816f1c65997b7306a9e199","tid":32224,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:41:45.000Z","msg":"整容失敗咁嘅樣"},{"pid":"76b3c80f736258b413a30b043243636f655cfcf3","tid":32224,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:41:55.000Z","msg":"高海寧混康華"},{"pid":"2b4f4a018970e338f436bf067e2e50d4bdd4340a","tid":32224,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:46:38.000Z","msg":"好大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469b870964de3f55138cc6b4d0701d63d9952692","tid":32224,"uid":56501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:03:48.000Z","msg":"巫女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc4b8dbe09beb7a663dbf01e1450d2fabdfb35f","tid":32224,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:07:13.000Z","msg":"我覺得幾正喎又有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496c3219b3ce5d955fb03b70ec7d7d65f13c3b44","tid":32224,"uid":23221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:20:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對波大到呢目測有D </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c29727000d3eb7aeacd2b6c6886e9dae0cebfaf","tid":32224,"uid":3268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy